I never got to actually taste it on ice cream because it was eaten up before then. It's also very good if you eat it from a jar. Be careful though if you reheat it. You must let it naturally come to room temperature before you stick it in the refridgerator or else it becomes grainy (I think it's something to do with the sugar molecules). I will assume it tastes excellent on ice cream though.

